## 🛠️ Technical Implementation Summary
- **Geospatial Backend**: Integrated Haversine formula for server-side distance calculations and updated [ServiceDto](file:///c:/Users/pruthviraj/OneDrive/Desktop/jdk/LocalConnect/backend/src/main/java/com/nearnest/dto/ServiceDto.java#7-104) with precise coordinate mapping.
- **Interactive Map Engine**: Custom React Google Maps integration with multi-marker support, InfoWindows, and two-way state synchronization.
- **Places Autocomplete**: Integrated Google Places API for seamless location searching.
- **Resilient Fallback**: Implemented a "Mock Discovery Mode" that maintains a premium interactive experience even without an active Google Maps API key.
- **Premium UX**: Modern side-by-side layout with glassmorphic controls and smooth Framer Motion animations.
